#

Roasted Beet and Goat Cheese Salad with Candied Walnuts and Citrus Vinaigrette

$12.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

NutsDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Tags:

SaladHealthyGourmet

Description

A vibrant salad featuring earthy roasted beets, creamy goat cheese, and sweet candied walnuts, drizzled with a zesty citrus vinaigrette.

Ingredients

  • Beets: 4 medium
  • Goat cheese: 150 grams
  • Walnuts: 100 grams
  • Brown sugar: 50 grams
  • Butter: 30 grams
  • Mixed salad greens: 200 grams
  • Orange juice: 4 tablespoons
  • Olive oil: 3 tablespoons
  • Dijon mustard: 1 tablespoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
